Package eu.datacrop.maize.model_repository.commons.dtos.responses.auxiliaries

Class KvAttributeResponseDto

java.lang.Object
eu.datacrop.maize.model_repository.commons.dtos.responses.auxiliaries.KvAttributeResponseDto
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class KvAttributeResponseDto extends Object implements Serializable
This class is a data transfer object representing KvAttributes, in essence additional parameters describing Assets. Used in HTTP responses.
Since:
version 0.4.0
Author:
Angela-Maria Despotopoulou [Athens, Greece]
